Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.49,0:00:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they're broken? But I hid them!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they dried up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I worked so hard to make them!\NAnd they were so shiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't cry, Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Go away, idiot Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all the same to me\Nwhether you're here or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, check out that tan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was in cram school all summer,\Nso I didn't have any fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to take the entrance exam for\NOkutsu College of Music Affiliated High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's in another prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I have permission from my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For famous music schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's all about how you ranked in competitions\Nand who your instructor is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I might not make the cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So my piano teacher said\NI should look into going overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That she'd introduce me to a friend\Nfrom when she was studying abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're thinking global!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.09,0:03:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leave the prefecture, leave the country.\NGo wherever you want, for all I care!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You moron, it's all the same to me\Nwhether you're around or not...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it's all the same to you\Nwhether I'm here or not...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the type\Nwho can't hide her uncertainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6 meters, 21 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can read you like a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap! That's a school record!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're covered in scrapes and bruises.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Band-Aid on your forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are laughing too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm humiliated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Freakin' scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki's been acting weird lately,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen to you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you leave her alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, excuse me for my horrible face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For being covered with Band-Aids!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Laughing at me with that\N nonchalant look on his face!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was hoping you'd praise me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm leaving home.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Talking to you either makes me feel sad,\Nor it sets my mind at ease...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm such a mess... How lame is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.97,0:04:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tsubaki?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just that your feet are huge.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you trying to jinx yourself by chanting\Nthat "kid brother, kid brother" curse?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're too scared not to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I met someone that I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See, she's older,\Nthe manager of the baseball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's really grounded, and she's got long hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's the kind of person\Nwho eats potato chips with chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on, you know we're too alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're both infielders, we've got\Nshort hair, and we're both rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you always seem so uncomfortable\Nbeing by my side, Sawabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.46,0:06:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're always laughing\Nlike you don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should be with people who are\Nthe total opposite, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.14,0:06:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our style to get all emotional, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's be ourselves breaking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?\NI'm the one who's dumping you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you apologizing, Sawabe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Sawabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For being my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scoot over, I've got to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push me! I'll fall off the bench!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard the piano making some\Nstrange sounds. So it was you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not asking me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to talk about it, I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just got dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was an older guy\Nthat I've always looked up to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So good-looking and sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was like premium ice cream to me.\NNo, not like ice cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.93,0:08:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More like a fancy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.31,0:08:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,120 ml...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.31,0:08:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The kind of ice cream that's not my style.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He told me he liked me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got ahead of myself...\NI got stubborn...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then I got dumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...ended up hurting that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot,\NI had no idea about my own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I'd never realized...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because I wanted things to go on just like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I missed my chance to become a star.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd like to take the entrance exam for\NOkutsu College of Music Affiliated High School.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time keeps flowing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both Watari...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.87,0:09:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Kousei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if they're afraid,\Neven if it's painful,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even if they can't see ahead,\Nstill seeking something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:10:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they take one step after another,\Nmustering the courage to go on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}inspiring each other, supporting\Neach other, they try to move on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.05,0:10:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the only one who can't take that first step.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Time does stop, doesn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the only one who's frozen in time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem anyway?\NAll you do is play the piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Music nerd! Can't you at least try\Nto comfort me, you useless jerk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all the same to me\Nwhether you're around or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it's all the same to you\Nwhether I'm here or not...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:11:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's so unfair! Being so nice\Nto a girl who just got dumped...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm being nice to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.95,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm treating you the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always by my side whenever I was in pain,\Nwhenever I was feeling sad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The boy who's not my kid brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll stay with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Liar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.84,0:11:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the one who's leaving me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It might be too late now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.09,0:11:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I don't want to give up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I may be an infielder, and rough, and I\Nmay not know anything about the piano,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I want to be with this person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.15,0:11:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hate music with a passion.\NIt's always taking Kousei far away from me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that, Tsubaki! The moon's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.12,0:11:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NWhat's that got to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I told you, don't be nice to me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't snuggle up against me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take the plunge, Tsubaki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time I exist in...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Start flowing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emi-rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bewitching!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're certainly training\Nan intriguing girl, Ms. Ochiai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When young talent collides, they polish\Neach other until they each achieve a sheen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please thank Arima-kun for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just you wait, Arima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:13:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't look back - move forward!\NFar, far ahead...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I swear I'm gonna catch up to you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to visit her in the hospital,\Nso what's there to worry about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A crow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A black cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Evil omens...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go see her another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All you do is make excuses.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The instant there's a little distance\Nbetween us, it gets harder to see you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.73,0:13:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I didn't think twice\Nabout seeing you in the music room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I'm searching for reasons\Nto see you, and not to see you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A water balloon!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Konnyaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A bucket?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Evil omens, like I thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Suffer! Suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud, Kousei,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.98,MSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seto
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,would you mind not getting things to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not good for Koharu to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's getting things to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like burgers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:38.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's come to. Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:45.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a sweet girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.00,0:14:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That boy over there brought you home,\Nlike takeout, when you fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you did get her to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's getting things to go? Like pot stickers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, by any chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.76,0:14:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Hiroko Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I should've introduced myself sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a first year in the music course at\NKurumigaoka Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Nagi Aizato.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's a prestigious music school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm studying piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pianist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was a pianist doing up in a tree?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a huge fan of yours, Ms. Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me as student!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mm, you've kind of put me on the spot here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be right\Nto do that to your own teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could you convince me with your playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The way you carry yourself is first-rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to play Chopin?\NOr maybe Bach?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, Etude Op. 25 No. 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The piece Kousei played\Nat the Maihou Competition...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... Why is she playing it so harshly?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A song like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A song like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd expect no less from\NKurumigaoka Junior High...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are first years today really\Ncapable of playing like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure can play at a high level.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe my idol, Ms. Seto,\Nis going to give me lessons...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.05,BTSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Eyedrops
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sneaked in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You teach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No black cat or crow around.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got her a gift, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would be a shame\Nto let it go to waste... Uh-huh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.18,0:17:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm her accompanist,\Nso it's only natural that I'd go see her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Coming and going... I'm always\Nsearching for an excuse.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.94,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori Miyazono
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so she's totally soaked, from head to toe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then Nakamura from Class 2, see,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he's laughing so hard he's got snot\Ndripping from his nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.91,0:18:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then I burst into laughter, too, so hard\Nthat I had a little drip going, too. Of snot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you thinking, bringing canelés\Nto the daughter of a cake shop owner?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank goodness I didn't give them to her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm such an idiot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're so heartless!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watari-kun's always coming to see me,\Nso why don't you ever show up?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Monster!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? How...? I never gave you my number–
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was just thinking\Nthat I hadn't heard your voice lately.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, you're eating something, aren't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.67,0:18:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A canelé.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lucky you! I wish I could have a canelé.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring some to you sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Really? That's a promise, all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're just like a cat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I approach you, you turn tail\Nand head off, far away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you're hurt, you get all playful,\Nas if you were trying to share your pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why... I feel so much love for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd like to have my dad's canelés.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Promise me, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A canelé eaten at night\Nhas a slightly bitter, gentle taste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought her face looked familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nous... Nous... Canelé... Canelé... Nous, nous...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.61,0:20:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up! Stand up!\NYou're my legs, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up! Come on, stand up! Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:20.02,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Liar
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:43.70,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 16\NTwo of a Kind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:55.01,BTSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Watch Again Next Week!
